snippet.title: Cactus Bill
snippet.description:
How you going? I'm Bill & this is my channel that I created during lockdown 2020, here in Australia 🇦🇺
I assure you, I am as confused as you are! I can't even write this damn description.. I shudder at what I'm about to disclose..but..I'm stuck on this Katie Joy train from hell! I'm doing what I can to try wake her up, before it's too late..
IRL, I am a total hermit by day & a standup comedienne by night. 
🌵 ✋ 
If you have a video that you'd like Bill to react to, please send link via dm or email. Thank you (:
___
